title: Some minor improvements.
message:
Some minor improvements.

* make the apiLevel property lazy loaded
* use the conventional `value` name in the date picker setter.

title: Fix regression on newer devices where resizing the widget wasn't causing a redraw.
message: Fix regression on newer devices where resizing the widget wasn't causing a redraw.

title: Fix some issues after kotlin rewrite.
message:
Fix some issues after kotlin rewrite.

* Fix issues found by Android Studio code inspection
* Compare manual rewrite with automatic conversion tool results and make a few improvements based on that.
  - Use properties instead of getter/setter functions
  - Use `[]` instead of `{@link }` in javadoc
  - Fix some spelling errors
  - For one-line functions: use `=` instead of `{}`
* Use `java.lang.String.format` instead of `String.format` for java 1.5 compatibility.
* Use `const` for constants.
